11
00:01:34,070 --> 00:01:34,920
to the girl I love.

12
00:01:37,120 --> 00:01:38,870
Is all of this for me?

13
00:01:41,840 --> 00:01:42,680
Wait.

14
00:01:43,120 --> 00:01:44,230
