96
00:07:50,430 --> 00:07:52,920
Of course, I'm going to continue
running the school.

97
00:07:53,120 --> 00:07:54,030
I've always wanted

98
00:07:54,240 --> 00:07:56,180
to prove myself through my career.

99
00:07:56,290 --> 00:07:57,730
