117
00:08:45,200 --> 00:08:46,720
His life is really valuable.

118
00:08:47,240 --> 00:08:48,670
He's constantly ruining our plans.

119
00:08:49,790 --> 00:08:50,790
He must be killed.

120
00:08:51,720 --> 00:08:53,630
